            <h3 class="text-primaryBlue mb-2 text-xl font-bold">HVAC Validation</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray mb-4 list-inside list-disc">
              <li>DOP/PAO filter testing</li>
              <li>Airflow & particle testing</li>
              <li>ISO 14644 compliance</li>
              <li>Cleanroom classification</li>
            </ul>
            <BTN btnLink="/services/hvac-validation" btnClass="buttonSimple" btnText="Read more‚Ä¶" />
          </div>

          <!-- Validation Documentation & Compliance -->
          <div class="bg-secondary-light2 border-gray rounded-lg border p-6 shadow-md">
            <div class="text-primary mb-4 text-4xl">üìú</div>
            <h3 class="text-primaryBlue mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Validation Documentation</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray mb-4 list-inside list-disc">
              <li>VMP & protocol preparation</li>
              <li>GAMP 5 risk planning</li>
              <li>Traceability & summary reports</li>
              <li>Audit readiness support</li>
            </ul>
            <BTN btnLink="/services/validation-documentation" btnClass="buttonSimple" btnText="Read more‚Ä¶" />
          </div>

          <!-- Training & Consultation -->
          <div class="bg-secondary-light2 border-gray rounded-lg border p-6 shadow-md">
            <div class="text-primary mb-4 text-4xl">üéì</div>
            <h3 class="text-primaryBlue mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Validation Training</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray mb-4 list-inside list-disc">
              <li>CSV & GAMP 5 training</li>
              <li>Data integrity (ALCOA+)</li>
              <li>Validation strategy workshops</li>
              <li>GxP system training</li>
            </ul>
            <BTN btnLink="/services/validation-training" btnClass="buttonSimple" btnText="Read more‚Ä¶" />
          </div>

          <!-- Periodic Review & Revalidation -->
          <div class="bg-secondary-light2 border-gray rounded-lg border p-6 shadow-md">
            <div class="text-primary mb-4 text-4xl">üîÑ</div>
            <h3 class="text-primaryBlue mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Periodic Review & Revalidation</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray mb-4 list-inside list-disc">
              <li>Periodic system reviews</li>
              <li>Trigger-based revalidation</li>
              <li>System decommissioning</li>
              <li>Change control integration</li>
            </ul>
            <BTN btnLink="/services/periodic-revalidation" btnClass="buttonSimple" btnText="Read more‚Ä¶" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Process Section -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-primaryBlue mb-6 text-3xl font-semibold">Our Validation Process</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-primaryBlue text-xl font-semibold">System Assessment</h3>
              <p class="text-gray">
                We evaluate systems (lab, automation, HVAC, etc.) to define validation scope and regulatory
                requirements.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-primaryBlue text-xl font-semibold">Protocol Development</h3>
              <p class="text-gray">
                We create Validation Master Plans, DQ/IQ/OQ/PQ protocols, and risk assessments per GAMP 5.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-primaryBlue text-xl font-semibold">Execution & Testing</h3>
              <p class="text-gray">
                We execute validation protocols, including testing for functionality, data integrity, and compliance.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-primaryBlue text-xl font-semibold">Documentation & Reporting</h3>
              <p class="text-gray">We provide traceability matrices, summary reports, and audit-ready documentation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">5</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-primaryBlue text-xl font-semibold">Ongoing Support</h3>
              <p class="text-gray">
                We offer periodic reviews, revalidation, and training to maintain compliance and system performance.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Compliance & Guidelines -->
      <section class="bg-secondary-light2 mb-12 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-primaryBlue mb-6 text-3xl font-semibold">Compliance & Standards</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-primaryBlue mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Regulatory Bodies</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray list-inside list-disc">
              <li>FDA (U.S. Food and Drug Administration)</li>
              <li>EMA (European Medicines Agency)</li>
              <li>ICH (International Council for Harmonisation)</li>
              <li>CDSCO (Central Drugs Standard Control Organization)</li>
              <li>WHO, PIC/S, TGA</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-primaryBlue mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Guidelines & Certifications</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray list-inside list-disc">
              <li>21 CFR Part 11, EU Annex 11</li>
              <li>GAMP 5, ICH Q2</li>
              <li>ISO 14644-1/2 (Cleanrooms)</li>
              <li>WHO TRS Annexes</li>
              <li>ISPE Guidelines</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-primaryBlue mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Applications & Industries</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray list-inside list-disc">
              <li>Pharmaceutical Manufacturing</li>
              <li>Biotechnology</li>
              <li>Contract Research Organizations</li>
              <li>Medical Device Manufacturing</li>
              <li>Quality Assurance/Control</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Conclusion -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-primaryBlue mb-4 text-3xl font-semibold">Why Choose Our Validation Services?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Our CRO delivers expert validation services for laboratory, automation, HVAC, and enterprise systems, ensuring
          compliance with global standards like 21 CFR Part 11, GAMP 5, and ISO 14644. With a risk-based approach and
          comprehensive documentation, we help you maintain system integrity and pass regulatory inspections. Partner
          with us to ensure your systems are robust, compliant, and ready for operational excellence.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <div class="bg-secondary-light border-secondary mb-12 border p-6 text-center">
      <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold">Ready to Validate Your Critical Systems?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray mb-4">Partner with us for compliant, reliable validation solutions.</p>
      <BTN btnLink="/contact-us" btnClass="button" btnText="Contact Us Today" />
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <Faq faqs={mainEntity} />
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
